which gives it its creamy finish,

39:18.259 --> 39:20.828
- and the machine used...
- Does it not seem strange to you?

39:22.196 --> 39:26.000
No, I mean... not really, no.

39:29.704 --> 39:30.604
I...

39:36.043 --> 39:37.044
Why do you hate him?

39:45.720 --> 39:47.188
That stuff is delicious, man.

39:59.033 --> 40:00.634
