41:51.679 --> 41:53.614
that he was working
for Grand Bath Martlin.

41:53.981 --> 41:55.716
<i>The government contractor.</i>

42:02.456 --> 42:03.991
Hey, what for the hell
are you doing?

42:04.024 --> 42:05.659
- Do it!
- No, don't do it.

42:05.693 --> 42:07.128
Do it!

42:09.497 --> 42:11.699
Are you fucking kidding me?

42:11.732 --> 42:13.901
You got to go to a hospital
to take that thing off.

42:13.934 --> 42:16.871
