to that hospital again.

42:16.904 --> 42:18.973
- Ever.
- Oh, it stinks.

42:20.975 --> 42:23.410
- Why aren't you at school?
- Sick.

42:26.313 --> 42:27.915
I got to go to work.

42:27.948 --> 42:29.717
Put an ace bandage on that thing
or something.

42:30.284 --> 42:32.853
- Ridiculous.
- Oh, it's so...

42:33.354 --> 42:34.655
...weak.

42:35.322 --> 42:36.824
And pale.

43:05.386 --> 43:06.287
Don't you agree?

43:08.455 --> 43:12.393
Uh, yeah. Uh, completely.
Absolutely.

43:12.426 --> 43:17.064
It's not like I want to be a
librarian, but I'm just there.

43:17.531 --> 43:18.866
Until I sort things out.

43:19.833 --> 43:23.204
Plus... I love being
surrounded by books.

43:24.471 --> 43:27.141
- Who wouldn't?
- Alright.

43:27.174 --> 43:29.910
You are all set back.

43:30.844 --> 43:31.745
There you go.

43:32.980 --> 43:34.215
Fantastic.

43:34.815 --> 43:35.883
Thank you, Lily.

43:36.150 --> 43:37.318
Hey, uh,

43:37.785 --> 43:39.453
you could always be a nurse.

43:40.888 --> 43:42.323
Fantastic.

43:42.990 --> 43:44.158
Thank you, Lily.

43:45.059 --> 43:47.895
Uh, you can always be a nurse.

43:51.232 --> 43:53.400
Are you ok... Are you okay?
What's wrong?

43:55.002 --> 43:57.371
Did I...

43:58.405 --> 44:05.012
Did I just thank you twice in
a row like exactly the same way?

44:06.213 --> 44:09.416
No. No, just once.

44:10.217 --> 44:11.518
Very nicely.

44:14.321 --> 44:16.190
I'm sorry. It's just...

44:18.092 --> 44:21.528
Still getting
my wits about me.

44:22.563 --> 44:23.464
Yeah, it's okay.

44:24.999 --> 44:26.133
You're doing great.

44:32.006 --> 44:33.440
Do you need anything
before I go?

44:39.046 --> 44:41.448
Well, I am heading
to the library.

44:41.482 --> 44:42.383
I'll see you later.

44:56.063 --> 44:58.399
<i>What made you join the military?</i>

44:58.866 --> 45:00.167
<i>Oh, I was recruited.</i>

45:01.368 --> 45:04.204
<i>The marines, they were
starting a new clandestine unit.</i>

45:04.238 --> 45:06.073
<i>Very small. Very secret.</i>

45:07.742 --> 45:11.378
<i>And they needed, uh, ten men total,
ten men in the whole country.</i>

45:12.647 --> 45:15.015
<i>So they, uh, they went
searching coast to coast.</i>

45:15.049 --> 45:16.850
<i>Wrangled up
about 100 candidates,</i>

45:16.884 --> 45:21.155
<i>and sent us up, uh,
it was up north to Alaska.</i>

45:21.922 --> 45:24.024
<i>Nine months of torture.
