45:24.659 --> 45:27.194
<i>It makes the SEALs look like
nap time at a nursery school.</i>

45:28.195 --> 45:31.031
<i>I really don't know how
I survived it, in fact, uh,</i>

45:31.398 --> 45:33.300
<i>there was a few
recruits that I know...</i>

45:36.570 --> 45:37.471
<i>Sorry.</i>

45:38.640 --> 45:42.042
<i>Uh, there was, uh,
a few young men who died</i>

45:42.076 --> 45:45.045
<i>the first week there on the
