45:47.047 --> 45:49.416
<i>Anyhow, the last ten
bastards standing</i>

45:49.450 --> 45:52.486
<i>all happened to be Ivy Leaguers
with backgrounds of science.</i>

45:53.420 --> 45:55.289
<i>And it was mostly plastics.</i>

45:56.423 --> 45:57.891
<i>Plastics?</i>

45:59.259 --> 46:01.929
<i>And is that... is that the work
you do now? Uh, plastics?</i>

46:02.396 --> 46:04.398
<i>Yes. So... some plastics.</i>

46:04.965 --> 46:09.970
<i>Some of the work is also with,
