53:12.860 --> 53:17.665
- Yes. Are you kidding me?
- Totally.

53:19.100 --> 53:20.768
Okay, if you're sure.

53:28.508 --> 53:33.547
Hey, listen, uh, I think Eddie has
a detention again today and, uh...

53:34.548 --> 53:36.583
He might be getting out soon.
